STRONGER targeted truck->car attack on 20 truck images (DEVICE=cpu)
Params: EPS=0.0627, ALPHA=0.0078, ITERS=120, CW_ITERS=150, MARGIN=5.0
Head layout @640px: strides [8, 16, 32], anchors/head [6400, 1600, 400], total 8400
NOTE: model cls outputs are sigmoid PROBS -> MARGIN=5.0 is inert (see report).

FLIP DEFINITION: a ground-truth TRUCK counts as 'flipped' iff the detector
  outputs a CAR (conf>=0.25) whose box has IoU>=0.5 with that
  truck's box -- i.e. a car AT the truck's location, NOT merely any car in the image.
  Image-level flip = at least one of that image's trucks is flipped.

